claim: The Rolling Stones sold the album Let It Bleed.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The album contained seven tracks from their second UK album The Rolling Stones No. 2 , the recent US Top 20 hit `` Heart of Stone '' , the recent UK No. 1 hit single `` Little Red Rooster '' , `` Surprise , Surprise '' , from The Lord 's Taverners Charity Album , `` Mona  (  I Need You Baby  )  '' from The Rolling Stones and `` Oh Baby  (  We Got A Good Thing Goin '  )  '' which would appear on the UK edition of the Stones ' next album Out of Our Heads later in 1965 .
